@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>Fargo Animal Shelter</h1>
        <p>Adopt a best friend today!</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/adopt">Adopt a Dog</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <section>
        <h2>Our Adoption Process</h2>
        <p>Our adoption process is very simple. We want to make your process as smooth as possible. Here are the first steps:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Search for currently available dogs using the filters.</li>
            <li>Apply online for a background check.</li>
            <li>Our team will review your application and send you an email after approval.</li>
            <li>Meet and play with your new best friend.</li>
            <li>Complete the adoption form and pay the $40 adoption fee and take your new dog home!</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Search for Dogs</h2>
        <p>Use the filters below to find the dog you want:</p>
        <!-- Add search filters here -->
        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="breed">Breed</label>
                <input type="text" id="breed" name="breed" placeholder="Enter breed">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="age">Age</label>
                <select id="age" name="age">
                    <option value="puppy">Puppy</option>
                    <option value="adult">Adult</option>
                    <option value="senior">Senior</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <button type="submit">Search</button>
        </form>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    header {
        text-align: center;
    }

    nav ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        text-align: center;
    }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

            nav ul li a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #007bff;
            }

                nav ul li a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }

    .form-group {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .form-group input, .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

    button {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
</style>